    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="duk.00492.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1892-01-12">12 Jan '92<ptr target="duk.00492_n1"/></date>
                    <name type="place">Studio 21 Pearl St.</name>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Our dear Friend and veritable Brother</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
                How regularly your kindly notes have cheered and sustained us. 
                When you were reported to be utterly failing, I still encouraged 
                her<ptr target="n7033"/>&#8212;Yet you must be suffering greatly<ptr target="loc.02538_n4"/>&#8212;
            </p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Gratefully Yours&#8212;and not hopeless&#8212;</salute>
                <signed>Charlie</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
